Company Overview of Harris Associates Investment Trust - Oakmark Equity and Income Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Harris Associates Investment Trust - Oakmark Equity and Income Fund is an open-ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Harris Associates L.P. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. For its equity portion, the fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. For its fixed income portion, the fund invests in the government and corporate securities, rated within the two highest grades assigned by Moody's and S&P. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on f...
Harris Associates Investment Trust - Oakmark Equity and Income Fund is an open-ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Harris Associates L.P. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. For its equity portion, the fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. For its fixed income portion, the fund invests in the government and corporate securities, rated within the two highest grades assigned by Moody's and S&P. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors such as free cash flows and intelligent investment of excess cash, earnings that are growing and are reasonably predictable, high level of company management ownership, yield-to-maturity, liquidity, current yield, companies expected to grow shareholder value over time, management teams that think and act as owners and call risk to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index, Barclays U.S. Government/Credit Index, and Lipper Balanced Funds Index. It conducts in-house research to create its portfolio. Harris Associates Investment Trust - Oakmark Equity and Income Fund was formed on November 1, 1995 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


